N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 163.18 - Course approval periods

State Regulations

Course approvals shall be valid for 12 months or portion
thereof, commencing January 1st or a date thereafter and shall continue until

December 31st of each year. Notes
